<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white> I have a 24th Iksar Warrior and I have to say STA does play a part. Alot of things I kill ( alot of times solo ) will take me down to a bub of STA if not all the way down. Asside from the HP STA gives, I notice a diff with added STA. Even when it goes down to 2 bubs I notice a change in how fast I hit. Thats about all I got. Thanksss</font></td></tr></table>
